{"tid":1068521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲男在教室被女老師硬上　不甘受辱輕生亡","createTime":"2019-03-19T09:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T01:06:45.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"497a056967b169565d1e1e047d00cfa45b35e083","tid":1068521,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190319/640_ff84c29e64bbd77994ad263dc4919f8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190319%2F640_ff84c29e64bbd77994ad263dc4919f8b.jpg&h=625e5501&s={SIZE}\" />v<br />\n<br />\n18歲男學生被42歲已婚女老師硬上，自覺受到汙辱，在女老師被逮的1年後輕生亡。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，18歲男學生麥迪森(Corbin Madison)，是被42歲女老師惠塔克（Tennille Whitaker）強迫發生性關係的4名學生之一。麥迪森的父親控告學區的負責人，要求賠償45000美元(約140萬)<br />\n<br />\n惠塔克去年10月，因對學校員工跟4名未成年男學生伸出淫爪，遭判20年徒刑，即使有其他同事向校長報告，但是校方多次無視，且也沒採取措施保護學生。學校警衛指出，曾看到惠塔克跟學生在上鎖沒開燈的教室中，也有其他受害者指出，惠塔克會給他們禮物，並給他們喝酒藉此硬上。雖然惠塔克被判刑，不過麥迪森感到恐懼、焦慮、精神痛苦、屈辱，在2018年8月輕生。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.allfootballapp.com/www/M00/0B/AA/rB8qZFueZZSARfDiACTSQoP5Lvs567.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.allfootballapp.com%2Fwww%2FM00%2F0B%2FAA%2FrB8qZFueZZSARfDiACTSQoP5Lvs567.gif&h=d2527a38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"564972d8bddd84e31f583fd144151a7224993b86","tid":1068521,"uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cded14a4040d5ecd375372fac3a27263fa7c2a","tid":1068521,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2de2b733f3bbfa821e3ad5872058ac9ff1d6c732","tid":1068521,"uid":206895,"like":264,"dislike":4,"score":260,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19